<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <meta name="author" content="Courtney Crews">
  <meta name="description" content="A personal NFT mint.">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Antic+Didone&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:ital,wght@0,300..800;1,300..800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="./images/favicon.png">

  <title>work - c.m.crews</title>

    <style>
    /* Full-width black background for artwork section */
    .artwork-hero {
      background: #000;
      min-height: 85vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 3rem 0;
    }

    .artwork-container {
      width: 95%;
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .iframe-wrapper {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      padding-bottom: 56.25%; /* 16:9 aspect ratio for desktop */
      background: (20, 20, 20, 10);
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
    }

    .iframe-wrapper iframe {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      border: none;
    }

    .artwork-controls {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .hidden-message-section {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 2rem auto 0;
      padding: 2rem;
      background: transparent;
      border-radius: 0;
      border: none;
    }

    .hidden-message-section label {
      display: block;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #666;
      text-align: center;
    }

    #hidden-message-holder {
      color: whitesmoke;
      font-style: italic;
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .hash-controls-wrapper {
      padding: 1.5rem 5rem;  
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 1px solid #222;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .hash-display-section {
      text-align: center;
      color: #999;
      font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .hash-display-section label {
      display: block;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: #666;
    }

    #hash-display {
      color: whitesmoke;
      font-size: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    .button-group {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    /* Info section below */
    .info-section {
      background: whitesmoke;
      padding: 4rem 0;
    }

    .info-content {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 2rem;
      color: #aaa;
    }

    .info-content h2 {
      font-family: 'Antic Didone', serif;
      color: royalblue;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    .info-content p {
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .info-content strong {
      color: royalblue;
    }

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .artwork-hero {
        min-height: auto;
        padding: 2rem 0;
      }

        .iframe-wrapper {
        padding-bottom: 100%; /* 1:1 aspect ratio for mobile */
      }

      .artwork-container {
        width: 95%;
      }

      .button-group {
        flex-direction: column;
        width: 100%;
      }

      .button-group button {
        width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
  </head>

<body>
    <div class="navbar navbar-expand-lg">
      <%- include('header'); %>
    </div>

    <section class="artwork-hero">
    <div class="artwork-container">
      <div class="iframe-wrapper">
        <iframe id="preview-frame" src="/iframe.html?hash=7777777777777777" title="Mantic"></iframe>
      </div>

      <div class="artwork-controls">
        <div class="hidden-message-section">
          <label>Deciphered Message</label>
          <div id="hidden-message-holder">—</div>
        </div>

        <div class="hash-controls-wrapper">
          <div class="hash-display-section">
            <label>Current Hash</label>
            <div id="hash-display">7777777777777777</div>
          </div>
          <div class="button-group">
          <button id="keep-hash" type="button" class="custom-button">Refresh</button>
          <button id="new-hash" type="button" class="custom-button">New Hash</button>
        </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Info section -->
  <section class="info-section">
    <div class="info-content">
      <h2>Mantic</h2>
      
      <p>
        An exploration of ancient divination symbols through generative parametric curves. 
        Each iteration is uniquely determined by one of sixteen traditional geomantic figures, 
        creating variations of flowing, harmonic compositions.
      </p>

      <p>
        This piece translates the binary language of geomancy into visual poetry. 
        The sixteen classical figures—Via, Populus, Fortuna Major, and others—each 
        carry symbolic meaning that influences color, form, and motion in the composition.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>How it works:</strong> Each hash generates a unique variation based on one of the geomantic symbols. 
        The resulting artwork reflects the figure's inherent qualities through algorithmic interpretation 
        of color palettes, curve behaviors, and compositional structure. Use the "Refresh" button to 
        redraw the current variation, or "New Variation" to generate a completely different piece.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

    <footer>
      <%- include('footer'); %>
    </footer>
  
    <script type="module" src="/js/index.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  </body>
  
  </html>